<lb n="0185a09" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><note n="0185004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】麗本，【甲】享和二年刊長谷寺藏本</note>佛說七俱胝佛母心大准提陀羅
<lb n="0185a10" ed="T"/>尼經</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0185a11" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0185a12" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator"><note n="0185005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">大唐天竺三藏＝大周沙門【宋】，唐武周沙門【明】【甲】</note><note n="0185005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">大唐天竺三藏【大】，大周沙門【宋】，唐武周沙門【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185005"><lem wit="【大】">大唐天竺三藏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">大周沙門</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】">唐武周沙門</rdg></app>地婆訶羅譯</byline>
<lb n="0185a13" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0185a1301">爾時佛在舍衛國祇樹給孤獨園。是時世尊
<lb n="0185a14" ed="T"/>思惟觀察。<note n="0185006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">愍＋（念）【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0185006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">愍【大】，愍念【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185006"><lem wit="【大】">愍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">愍念</rdg></app>未來諸眾生故。說是七俱胝佛
<lb n="0185a15" ed="T"/>母心准提陀羅尼法。即說呪曰。</p>
<lb n="0185a16" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0185a1601" cb:type="dharani">南<note n="0185007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">謨＝無【明】【甲】</note><note n="0185007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">謨【大】，無【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185007"><lem wit="【大】">謨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】">無</rdg></app><note n="0185008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">颯＋（蘇臘反）細註【宋】</note><note n="0185008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">颯【大】，颯(蘇臘反)【宋】</note><app n="0185008"><lem wit="【大】">颯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">颯<note place="inline">蘇臘反</note></rdg></app><note n="0185009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">哆＋（都那反）細註【宋】</note><note n="0185009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">哆【大】，哆(都那反)【宋】</note><app n="0185009"><lem wit="【大】">哆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">哆<note place="inline">都那反</note></rdg></app>南<note place="inline"><note n="0185010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（奴誓反）＋一【宋】</note><note n="0185010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">一【大】，奴誓反一【宋】</note><app n="0185010"><lem wit="【大】">一</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">奴誓反一</rdg></app></note>三藐三<note n="0185011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">勃＋（蒲沒反）【宋】</note><note n="0185011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">勃【大】，勃蒲沒反【宋】</note><app n="0185011"><lem wit="【大】">勃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">勃蒲沒反</rdg></app>陀俱胝南<note place="inline"><note n="0185012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">二＝同上二句【宋】</note><note n="0185012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">二【大】，同上二句【宋】</note><app n="0185012"><lem wit="【大】">二</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">同上二句</rdg></app></note>
<lb n="0185a17" ed="T"/><note n="0185013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">怛＋（都捺反）【宋】</note><note n="0185013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">怛【大】，怛都捺反【宋】</note><app n="0185013"><lem wit="【大】">怛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">怛都捺反</rdg></app><note n="0185014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">姪＋（徒列反）【宋】</note><note n="0185014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">姪【大】，姪徒列反【宋】</note><app n="0185014"><lem wit="【大】">姪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">姪徒列反</rdg></app>他<note place="inline"><note n="0185015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（長引）＋三【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0185015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">三【大】，長引三【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185015"><lem wit="【大】">三</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">長引三</rdg></app></note>唵折戾<note place="inline"><note n="0185016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（之熱反）＋四【宋】</note><note n="0185016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">四【大】，之熱反四【宋】</note><app n="0185016"><lem wit="【大】">四</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">之熱反四</rdg></app></note>主戾<note place="inline"><note n="0185017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">五＝同上五句【宋】</note><note n="0185017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">五【大】，同上五句【宋】</note><app n="0185017"><lem wit="【大】">五</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">同上五句</rdg></app></note>准<note n="0185018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">締＝提【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0185018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">締【大】，提【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185018"><lem wit="【大】">締</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">提</rdg></app><note place="inline"><note n="0185019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">六＋（句）【宋】</note><note n="0185019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">六【大】，六句【宋】</note><app n="0185019"><lem wit="【大】">六</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">六句</rdg></app></note><note n="0185020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">娑＝莎【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0185020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">娑【大】，莎【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185020"><lem wit="【大】">娑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">莎</rdg></app>
<lb n="0185a18" ed="T"/>婆訶<note place="inline"><note n="0185021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">七＋（句）【宋】</note><note n="0185021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">七【大】，七句【宋】</note><app n="0185021"><lem wit="【大】">七</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">七句</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0185a19" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0185a1901">若有比丘比丘尼優婆塞優婆夷。受持讀誦
<lb n="0185a20" ed="T"/>此陀羅尼滿八十萬遍無量劫來所造五無間
<lb n="0185a21" ed="T"/>等。一切諸罪<note n="0185022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔皆〕－【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0185022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">皆【大】，〔－〕【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185022"><lem wit="【大】">皆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>悉<note n="0185023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔消〕－【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0185023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">消【大】，〔－〕【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185023"><lem wit="【大】">消</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app><note n="0185024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">滅＋（無餘）【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0185024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">滅【大】，滅無餘【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185024"><lem wit="【大】">滅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">滅無餘</rdg></app>。所在生處皆得
<lb n="0185a22" ed="T"/>值遇諸佛菩薩。所有資<note n="0185025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">具＋（隨具）【甲】</note><note n="0185025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">具【大】，具隨具【甲】</note><app n="0185025"><lem wit="【大】">具</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">具隨具</rdg></app>隨意充足。生生
<lb n="0185a23" ed="T"/>常得出家。具持菩薩律儀淨戒。恒生人天
<lb n="0185a24" ed="T"/>不墮惡趣。常為諸天之所守護。若有在家善
<lb n="0185a25" ed="T"/>男女等誦持之者。其家無有災橫病苦之所
<lb n="0185a26" ed="T"/>惱害。諸有所作無不諧偶。所<note n="0185026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">說＝出【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0185026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">說【大】，出【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185026"><lem wit="【大】">說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">出</rdg></app>言<note n="0185027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">語＝教【宋】【甲】</note><note n="0185027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">語【大】，教【宋】【甲】</note><app n="0185027"><lem wit="【大】">語</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【甲】">教</rdg></app>人皆
<lb n="0185a27" ed="T"/>信受。若有誦此陀羅尼呪滿十萬遍。夢中
<lb n="0185a28" ed="T"/>得見諸佛菩薩聲聞緣覺。自見口中<note n="0185028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">吐＝咄【甲】＊</note><note n="0185028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">吐【大】＊，咄【甲】＊</note><app n="0185028"><lem wit="【大】">吐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">咄</rdg></app>出黑
<lb n="0185a29" ed="T"/><note n="0185029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">物＝飯【宋】【明】【甲】＊</note><note n="0185029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">物【大】＊，飯【宋】【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0185029"><lem wit="【大】">物</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">飯</rdg></app>。若有重罪誦滿二十萬遍。夢中亦見諸
<pb n="0185b" xml:id="T20.1077.0185b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0185b01" ed="T"/>佛菩薩。亦<note n="0185030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔復〕－【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0185030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">復【大】，〔－〕【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185030"><lem wit="【大】">復</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>自<note n="0185031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">見＋（口中）【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0185031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">見【大】，見口中【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185031"><lem wit="【大】">見</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">見口中</rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#0185028"><lem wit="【大】">吐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">咄</rdg></app>出黑<app type="star" corresp="#0185029"><lem wit="【大】">物</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">飯</rdg></app>。若有五逆
<lb n="0185b02" ed="T"/><note n="0185032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">罪＋（者）【宋】【甲】</note><note n="0185032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">罪【大】，罪者【宋】【甲】</note><app n="0185032"><lem wit="【大】">罪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【甲】">罪者</rdg></app>。不得如是善夢<note n="0185033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">之者宜＝現時【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0185033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">之者宜【大】，現時【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185033"><lem wit="【大】">之者。宜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">現時</rdg></app>應更誦滿七十
<lb n="0185b03" ed="T"/>萬遍。是時還得如前之相。乃至夢見<app type="star" corresp="#0185028"><lem wit="【大】">吐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">咄</rdg></app>出
<lb n="0185b04" ed="T"/>白色<note n="0185034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">如酪飯等＝粳米酪飯【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0185034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">如酪飯等【大】，粳米酪飯【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185034"><lem wit="【大】">如酪飯等</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">粳米酪飯</rdg></app>。當知此人即是罪滅。清淨
<lb n="0185b05" ed="T"/>之相。</p>
<lb n="0185b06" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0185b0601">復次我今說<note n="0185035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">此＝之【明】【甲】</note><note n="0185035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">此【大】，之【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185035"><lem wit="【大】">此</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】">之</rdg></app>大陀羅尼所作之事。若於佛
<lb n="0185b07" ed="T"/>像前。或於塔前若清淨處。以瞿摩<note n="0185036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">夷＋（唐云牛糞）【宋】，（此云牛糞）【明】【甲】</note><note n="0185036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">夷【大】，夷唐云牛糞【宋】，<!--CBETA todo type: newmod-->夷此云牛糞【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185036"><lem wit="【大】">夷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">夷唐云牛糞</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】">夷此云牛糞</rdg></app>塗地。
<lb n="0185b08" ed="T"/>而作方壇隨其大小。復以花香幡蓋<note n="0185037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">飲＝飯【甲】</note><note n="0185037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">飲【大】，飯【甲】</note><app n="0185037"><lem wit="【大】">飲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">飯</rdg></app>食
<lb n="0185b09" ed="T"/><note n="0185038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">燈燭＝燈明燭火【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0185038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">燈燭【大】，燈明燭火【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185038"><lem wit="【大】">燈燭</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">燈明燭火</rdg></app>。隨力所辦而供養之。復呪香水散於四
<lb n="0185b10" ed="T"/><note n="0185039" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">方＋（及以）【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0185039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">方【大】，方及以【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185039"><lem wit="【大】">方</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">方及以</rdg></app>上下以為結<note n="0185040" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">界＋（既結界已）【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0185040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">界【大】，界既結界已【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185040"><lem wit="【大】">界</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">界既結界已</rdg></app>。於壇四角及壇中央。皆
<lb n="0185b11" ed="T"/>各置一香水之瓶。持呪之者於其壇中。面向
<lb n="0185b12" ed="T"/>東方<note n="0185041" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">胡＝䠒【甲】</note><note n="0185041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">胡【大】，䠒【甲】</note><app n="0185041"><lem wit="【大】">胡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">䠒</rdg></app>跪。誦呪一千<note n="0185042" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">八＋（十）【宋】【明】【甲】＊</note><note n="0185042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">八【大】＊，八十【宋】【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0185042"><lem wit="【大】">八</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">八十</rdg></app>遍。其香水瓶即便
<lb n="0185b13" ed="T"/>自<note n="0185043" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">轉＝輪【甲】</note><note n="0185043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">轉【大】，輪【甲】</note><app n="0185043"><lem wit="【大】">轉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">輪</rdg></app>。叉手捧雜花。呪<note n="0185044" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（一）＋千【宋】【明】【甲】＊</note><note n="0185044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">千【大】＊，一千【宋】【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0185044"><lem wit="【大】">千</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">一千</rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#0185042"><lem wit="【大】">八</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">八十</rdg></app>遍。散一鏡面。
<lb n="0185b14" ed="T"/>又於鏡前正<note n="0185045" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">觀＋（鏡面）【宋】【元】【甲】</note><note n="0185045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">觀【大】，觀鏡面【宋】【元】【甲】</note><app n="0185045"><lem wit="【大】">觀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【甲】">觀鏡面</rdg></app>。誦呪亦<app type="star" corresp="#0185044"><lem wit="【大】">千</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">一千</rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#0185042"><lem wit="【大】">八</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">八十</rdg></app><note n="0185046" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">遍＋（又以香油以蘇摩那花香浸著胡麻油中塗手大指誦呪一百八遍即於童面鏡中指爪甲內皆各）三十八字【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0185046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">遍【大】，遍又以香油以蘇摩那花香浸著胡麻油中塗手大指誦呪一百八遍即於童面鏡中指爪甲內皆各【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185046"><lem wit="【大】">遍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">遍又以香油以蘇摩那花香浸著胡麻油中塗手大指誦呪一百八遍即於童面鏡中指爪甲內皆各</rdg></app>。得見佛
<lb n="0185b15" ed="T"/>菩薩像。<note n="0185047" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">應＝復誦呪【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0185047" resp="CBETA" type="mod">應【大】，復誦呪【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185047"><lem wit="【大】">應</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">復誦呪</rdg></app>呪花<note n="0185048" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（一）＋百【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0185048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">百【大】，一百【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185048"><lem wit="【大】">百</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">一百</rdg></app>八遍。而散供<note n="0185049" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">養＋（佛菩薩像心所有事一一）十字【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0185049" resp="CBETA" type="mod">養【大】，養佛菩薩像心所有事一一【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185049"><lem wit="【大】">養</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">養佛菩薩像心所有事一一</rdg></app>。<note n="0185050" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔隨〕－【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0185050" resp="CBETA" type="mod">隨【大】，〔－〕【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185050"><lem wit="【大】">隨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>請
<lb n="0185b16" ed="T"/>問<note n="0185051" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔法〕－【宋】【甲】</note><note n="0185051" resp="CBETA" type="mod">法【大】，〔－〕【宋】【甲】</note><app n="0185051"><lem wit="【大】">法</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>無不決了。若有鬼病以<note n="0185052" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">呪＋（呪）【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0185052" resp="CBETA" type="mod">呪【大】，呪呪【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185052"><lem wit="【大】">呪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">呪呪</rdg></app>茅<note n="0185053" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">草＝得香茅第一不得直茅亦得（細註）【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0185053" resp="CBETA" type="mod">草【大】，(得香茅第一不得直茅亦得)【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185053"><lem wit="【大】">草</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】"><note place="inline">得香茅第一不得直茅亦得</note></rdg></app>而拂
<lb n="0185b17" ed="T"/>病人即得除愈。若有幼小為鬼所著。以五色
<lb n="0185b18" ed="T"/>縷應令童女<note n="0185054" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">搓＝合【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0185054" resp="CBETA" type="mod">搓【大】，合【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185054"><lem wit="【大】">搓</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">合</rdg></app>以<note n="0185055" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">為＝成【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0185055" resp="CBETA" type="mod">為【大】，成【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185055"><lem wit="【大】">為</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">成</rdg></app>線。一呪一結滿二十
<lb n="0185b19" ed="T"/><note n="0185056" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">一＋（結）【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0185056" resp="CBETA" type="mod">一【大】，一結【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185056"><lem wit="【大】">一</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">一結</rdg></app>。用繫其頸。<note n="0185057" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">以＋（白）【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0185057" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以【大】，以白【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185057"><lem wit="【大】">以</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">以白</rdg></app>芥子呪<note n="0185058" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">滿＝之【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0185058" resp="CBETA" type="mod">滿【大】，之【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185058"><lem wit="【大】">滿</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">之</rdg></app>七遍。<note n="0185059" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（復）＋散【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0185059" resp="CBETA" type="mod">散【大】，復散【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185059"><lem wit="【大】">散</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">復散</rdg></app>其面
<lb n="0185b20" ed="T"/>即便除<note n="0185060" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">差＝瘥【宋】【明】【甲】＊</note><note n="0185060" resp="CBETA" type="mod">差【大】＊，瘥【宋】【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0185060"><lem wit="【大】">差</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">瘥</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0185b21" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0185b2101">復次有法。於病者<note n="0185061" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">前＋（以）【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0185061" resp="CBETA" type="mod">前【大】，前以【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185061"><lem wit="【大】">前</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">前以</rdg></app>墨畫其<note n="0185062" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">形＝病人形像【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0185062" resp="CBETA" type="mod">形【大】，病人形像【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185062"><lem wit="【大】">形</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">病人形像</rdg></app>。呪楊枝打
<lb n="0185b22" ed="T"/><note n="0185063" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">之＝此畫形【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0185063" resp="CBETA" type="mod">之【大】，此畫形【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185063"><lem wit="【大】">之</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">此畫形</rdg></app>。亦<note n="0185064" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">便＝得【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0185064" resp="CBETA" type="mod">便【大】，得【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185064"><lem wit="【大】">便</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">得</rdg></app>除<app type="star" corresp="#0185060"><lem wit="【大】">差</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">瘥</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0185b23" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0185b2301">復<note n="0185065" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">次有＝有一【宋】【明】【甲】＊</note><note n="0185065" resp="CBETA" type="mod">次有【大】＊，有一【宋】【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0185065"><lem wit="【大】">次有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">有一</rdg></app>法。若有病人為鬼所著身在遠處。
<lb n="0185b24" ed="T"/>應呪楊枝<note n="0185066" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">具＝足【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0185066" resp="CBETA" type="mod">具【大】，足【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185066"><lem wit="【大】">具</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">足</rdg></app>滿七遍。寄<note n="0185067" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">人＝往【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0185067" resp="CBETA" type="mod">人【大】，往【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185067"><lem wit="【大】">人</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">往</rdg></app>持打即亦除
<lb n="0185b25" ed="T"/><note n="0185068" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">差＝愈【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0185068" resp="CBETA" type="mod">差【大】，愈【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185068"><lem wit="【大】">差</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">愈</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0185b26" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0185b2601">復<app type="star" corresp="#0185065"><lem wit="【大】">次有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">有一</rdg></app>法。若在路行<note n="0185069" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">誦＋（念）【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0185069" resp="CBETA" type="mod">誦【大】，誦念【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185069"><lem wit="【大】">誦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">誦念</rdg></app>此呪。無有賊盜惡
<lb n="0185b27" ed="T"/>獸等<note n="0185070" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">畏＝怖【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0185070" resp="CBETA" type="mod">畏【大】，怖【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185070"><lem wit="【大】">畏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">怖</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0185b28" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0185b2801">復<app type="star" corresp="#0185065"><lem wit="【大】">次有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">有一</rdg></app>法。常持此呪。設有諍訟無不獲勝。
<lb n="0185b29" ed="T"/>若欲往渡江河大海。誦呪而渡無有水中惡
<pb n="0185c" xml:id="T20.1077.0185c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0185c01" ed="T"/>獸等難。</p>
<lb n="0185c02" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0185c0201">復<app type="star" corresp="#0185065"><lem wit="【大】">次有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">有一</rdg></app>法。若被繫閉枷鎖<note n="0185071" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">禁＋（繫）【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0185071" resp="CBETA" type="mod">禁【大】，禁繫【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185071"><lem wit="【大】">禁</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">禁繫</rdg></app>其身。誦此呪
<lb n="0185c03" ed="T"/>者即得解脫。</p>
<lb n="0185c04" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0185c0401">復<note n="0185072" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">次有＝有一【宋】【明】，一【甲】</note><note n="0185072" resp="CBETA" type="mod">次有【大】，有一【宋】【明】，一【甲】</note><app n="0185072"><lem wit="【大】">次有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】">有一</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">一</rdg></app>法若諸國土水旱不調。疫毒流<note n="0185073" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">行＋（應行）【甲】</note><note n="0185073" resp="CBETA" type="mod">行【大】，行應行【甲】</note><app n="0185073"><lem wit="【大】">行</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">行應行</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0185c05" ed="T"/>應以酥和胡麻粳米。用手三指取其一撮。呪
<lb n="0185c06" ed="T"/>之一遍<note n="0185074" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">置＝擲【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0185074" resp="CBETA" type="mod">置【大】，擲【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185074"><lem wit="【大】">置</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">擲</rdg></app>火中燒。或經七日七夜。六時如是
<lb n="0185c07" ed="T"/>相續不絕。一切災疫<note n="0185075" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">悉皆＝無不【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0185075" resp="CBETA" type="mod">悉皆【大】，無不【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185075"><lem wit="【大】">悉皆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">無不</rdg></app>消<note n="0185076" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">滅＋（復有一法以酥和稻穀呪一百八遍火中燒之隨心所願無不成諦財寶增盈求心滿足若人欲令他敬念者稱彼前人名字一呪一稱滿一百八遍即便敬念）六十一字【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0185076" resp="CBETA" type="mod">滅【大】，滅復有一法以酥和稻穀呪一百八遍火中燒之隨心所願無不成諦財寶增盈求心滿足若人欲令他敬念者稱彼前人名字一呪一稱滿一百八遍即便敬念【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185076"><lem wit="【大】">滅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">滅復有一法以酥和稻穀呪一百八遍火中燒之隨心所願無不成諦財寶增盈求心滿足若人欲令他敬念者稱彼前人名字一呪一稱滿一百八遍即便敬念</rdg></app>。</p>
<pb n="0186a" xml:id="T20.1077.0186a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0186a01" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0186a0101">復<app type="star" corresp="#0185065"><lem wit="【大】">次有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">有一</rdg></app>法。於河渚間砂潬之上。<note n="0186001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">以＋（塗形像）【宋】【明】，（塔形形像）【甲】</note><note n="0186001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以【大】，以塗形像【宋】【明】，<!--CBETA todo type: newmod-->以塔形形像【甲】</note><app n="0186001"><lem wit="【大】">以</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】">以塗形像</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">以塔形形像</rdg></app>印。印
<lb n="0186a02" ed="T"/><note n="0186002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">砂＋（坦上）【宋】，（潬上）【明】【甲】</note><note n="0186002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">砂【大】，砂坦上【宋】，<!--CBETA todo type: newmod-->砂潬上【明】【甲】</note><app n="0186002"><lem wit="【大】">砂</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">砂坦上</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】">砂潬上</rdg></app>為塔形像。誦呪一遍印成一塔。<note n="0186003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（如是數）＋滿【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0186003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">滿【大】，如是數滿【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0186003"><lem wit="【大】">滿</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">如是數滿</rdg></app>六十
<lb n="0186a03" ed="T"/>萬遍。<note n="0186004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">或＝即得覩【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0186004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">或【大】，即得覩【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0186004"><lem wit="【大】">或</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">即得覩</rdg></app><note n="0186005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">見＋（聖者）【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0186005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">見【大】，見聖者【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0186005"><lem wit="【大】">見</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">見聖者</rdg></app>觀<note n="0186006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">世音＝自在【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0186006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">世音【大】，自在【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0186006"><lem wit="【大】">世音</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">自在</rdg></app>菩<note n="0186007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">薩＋（之像）【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0186007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">薩【大】，薩之像【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0186007"><lem wit="【大】">薩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">薩之像</rdg></app>。或見多羅菩薩。
<lb n="0186a04" ed="T"/><note n="0186008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔或見〕－【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0186008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">或見【大】，〔－〕【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0186008"><lem wit="【大】">或見</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>金剛<note n="0186009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">主＝手【甲】</note><note n="0186009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">主【大】，手【甲】</note><app n="0186009"><lem wit="【大】">主</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">手</rdg></app>菩薩。<note n="0186010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">隨＋（其）【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0186010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">隨【大】，隨其【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0186010"><lem wit="【大】">隨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">隨其</rdg></app>心<note n="0186011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">所求＝願【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0186011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">所求【大】，願【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0186011"><lem wit="【大】">所求</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">願</rdg></app>皆得滿足。
<lb n="0186a05" ed="T"/>或見授與<note n="0186012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">仙＋（神妙）【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0186012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">仙【大】，仙神妙【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0186012"><lem wit="【大】">仙</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">仙神妙</rdg></app>藥。或見<note n="0186013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">與受＝授與【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0186013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">與受【大】，授與【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0186013"><lem wit="【大】">與受</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">授與</rdg></app>菩提之記。</p>
<lb n="0186a06" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0186a0601">復<app type="star" corresp="#0185065"><lem wit="【大】">次有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">有一</rdg></app><note n="0186014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">法＋（作）【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0186014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">法【大】，法作【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0186014"><lem wit="【大】">法</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">法作</rdg></app>。右遶菩提樹像。誦呪滿千萬遍。
<lb n="0186a07" ed="T"/>即見菩薩為其說法。欲隨菩薩即得隨從。</p>
<lb n="0186a08" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0186a0801">復<app type="star" corresp="#0185065"><lem wit="【大】">次有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">有一</rdg></app>法。若乞食時常持此呪。不為惡人惡
<lb n="0186a09" ed="T"/>狗等類之所<note n="0186015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">惱＝侵【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0186015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">惱【大】，侵【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0186015"><lem wit="【大】">惱</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">侵</rdg></app>害。<note n="0186016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">若於＝復有一法若在【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0186016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">若於【大】，復有一法若在【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0186016"><lem wit="【大】">若於</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">復有一法若在</rdg></app>塔前或佛像前或
<lb n="0186a10" ed="T"/>舍利塔前。誦持此呪三十萬遍。<note n="0186017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔復〕－【甲】</note><note n="0186017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">復【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0186017"><lem wit="【大】">復</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>於白月
<lb n="0186a11" ed="T"/>十五日設大供養。一日一夜不食正<note n="0186018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔念〕－【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0186018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">念【大】，〔－〕【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0186018"><lem wit="【大】">念</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>誦呪。
<lb n="0186a12" ed="T"/><note n="0186019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔乃至〕－【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0186019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">乃至【大】，〔－〕【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0186019"><lem wit="【大】">乃至</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>得見金剛手菩薩。而彼菩薩即將是
<lb n="0186a13" ed="T"/><note n="0186020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔人〕－【甲】</note><note n="0186020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">人【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0186020"><lem wit="【大】">人</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>往於自宮。</p>
<lb n="0186a14" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0186a1401">復<app type="star" corresp="#0185065"><lem wit="【大】">次有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">有一</rdg></app>法。若於轉法輪塔前或佛生處塔前。
<lb n="0186a15" ed="T"/>或<note n="0186021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">從＝於【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0186021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">從【大】，於【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0186021"><lem wit="【大】">從</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">於</rdg></app>忉利天下寶階塔前或舍利塔前。於如
<lb n="0186a16" ed="T"/>是等諸塔之前誦呪右遶。即見阿鉢羅是多
<lb n="0186a17" ed="T"/>菩薩及訶利底菩薩。隨其所願皆悉滿足。若
<lb n="0186a18" ed="T"/>須仙藥即便授之。復為說法示菩薩道。若有
<lb n="0186a19" ed="T"/>誦此陀羅尼者。乃至未坐道場。一切菩薩<note n="0186022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔常〕－【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0186022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">常【大】，〔－〕【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0186022"><lem wit="【大】">常</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<lb n="0186a20" ed="T"/>為<note n="0186023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">善＝其勝【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0186023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">善【大】，其勝【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0186023"><lem wit="【大】">善</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">其勝</rdg></app>友。又此准提大陀羅尼大明呪法。過去
<lb n="0186a21" ed="T"/>一切諸佛已說。<note n="0186024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">未來一切諸佛當說∞現在一切諸佛今說【宋】【明】，〔未來…說〕八字－【甲】</note><note n="0186024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔－〕【甲】，未來一切諸佛當說【大】∞現在一切諸佛今說【宋】【明】</note><app n="0186024"><lem wit="【大】">未來一切諸佛當說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】">現在一切諸佛今說</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。<note n="0186025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">未來一切諸佛當說∞現在一切諸佛今說【宋】【明】，〔未來…說〕八字－【甲】</note><note n="0186025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">現在一切諸佛今說【大】∞未來一切諸佛當說【宋】【明】</note><app n="0186025"><lem wit="【大】">現在
<lb n="0186a22" ed="T"/>一切諸佛<note n="0186026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">今＝當【甲】</note><note n="0186026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">今【大】，當【甲】</note><app n="0186026"><lem wit="【大】">今</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">當</rdg></app>說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】">未來一切諸佛當說</rdg></app>。我今亦如是說。為利<note n="0186027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔益〕－【宋】【甲】</note><note n="0186027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">益【大】，〔－〕【宋】【甲】</note><app n="0186027"><lem wit="【大】">益</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>一
<lb n="0186a23" ed="T"/>切眾生故。<note n="0186028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔令〕－【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0186028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">令【大】，〔－〕【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0186028"><lem wit="【大】">令</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>得無上菩提故。若有薄福眾
<lb n="0186a24" ed="T"/>生。<note n="0186029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">無＋（有）【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0186029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">無【大】，無有【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0186029"><lem wit="【大】">無</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">無有</rdg></app>少善根者。無有根器之者。無有<note n="0186030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">菩提分法＝菩提分【宋】【明】，善根分【甲】</note><note n="0186030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">菩提分法【大】，菩提分【宋】【明】，善根分【甲】</note><app n="0186030"><lem wit="【大】">菩提
<lb n="0186a25" ed="T"/>分法</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】">菩提分</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">善根分</rdg></app>者。若得聞此<note n="0186031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（大准提）＋陀【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0186031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">陀【大】，大准提陀【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0186031"><lem wit="【大】">陀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">大准提陀</rdg></app>羅尼法。速疾證得阿耨
<lb n="0186a26" ed="T"/>多羅三藐三菩提。若有人<note n="0186032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">能常自憶＝憶持誦【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0186032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">能常自憶【大】，憶持誦【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0186032"><lem wit="【大】">能常自憶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">憶持誦</rdg></app>念。<note n="0186033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">誦持此呪＝常不懈廢此佛母心大准提陀羅尼者【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0186033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">誦持此呪【大】，常不懈廢此佛母心大准提陀羅尼者【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0186033"><lem wit="【大】">誦
<lb n="0186a27" ed="T"/>持此呪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">常不懈廢此佛母心大准提陀羅尼者</rdg></app>。無量善根皆得成就。佛說此大准提
<lb n="0186a28" ed="T"/>陀羅尼法時。無量眾生遠塵離垢。得大准提
<lb n="0186a29" ed="T"/>陀羅尼大明呪功德。得見十方諸佛菩<note n="0186034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">薩諸＝提【甲】</note><note n="0186034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">薩諸【大】，提【甲】</note><app n="0186034"><lem wit="【大】">薩諸</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">提</rdg></app>
<pb n="0186b" xml:id="T20.1077.0186b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0186b01" ed="T"/>聖眾<note n="0186035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">等＝向佛【甲】</note><note n="0186035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">等【大】，向佛【甲】</note><app n="0186035"><lem wit="【大】">等</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">向佛</rdg></app>作禮而去。</p>
